Notes: LITHIUM flow from FS-NA (North America) to XS-EU (Europe).
LITHIUM flow from XS-EU (Europe) to CT-AS (Asia).
LITHIUM flow from CT-AS (Asia) to FS-OC (Oceania).
LITHIUM flow from FS-OC (Oceania) to XS-AF (Africa).
LITHIUM flow from XS-AF (Africa) to CT-SA (South America).
LITHIUM flow from CT-SA (South America) to FS-NA (North America).
